{"tid":710275,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲佩斯：加盟曼聯後覺得自己終於在效力一支強隊","createTime":"2018-06-20T15:12:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T19:00:17.000Z","uid":165817,"like":56,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"767ecd285526f8ce83e4fa4002a8894f5a039494","tid":710275,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"　　近日，前曼聯後衛艾拉在接受專訪時回憶起雲佩斯當年加入曼聯的情景，前者描述了雲佩斯在聽到自己把阿仙奴描述成「嬰兒隊」之後的反應。<br />\n<br />\n　　「當雲佩斯剛加盟曼聯時，我跟他說：『歡迎來到一支合適的球隊，一支男人的球隊，而不是『嬰兒隊』。然後他就大笑了出來，但是他立刻就聽懂了。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我記得他說：『艾拉，老實說，我覺得自己正在為一支厲害的球隊踢球，因為你們所有人都贏了許多獎盃和獎牌，而且你們在訓練前和訓練後都堅持要進入健身房。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「雲佩斯就像個小孩一樣，他好像對這一點感到驚訝。他看到我們時就會說：『看著你們，我必須刻苦努力，因為我想贏球，我想贏得一些獎盃。』」"},{"pid":"585dc41d6b62cfe3d6f562b5f183c203aa6138e3","tid":710275,"uid":71694,"like":36,"dislike":3,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:14:22.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦，無爺爺你有今日？"},{"pid":"851004c6f0f91747ffe5983a88003ae1147f4451","tid":710275,"uid":41961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"幾時做埋曼聯明叔"},{"pid":"74b344ec76956a2075ce0635347ee57cc26e3c9b","tid":710275,"uid":165817,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"851004c6f0f91747ffe5983a88003ae1147f4451","tid":710275,"uid":41961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"幾時做埋曼聯明叔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T15:25:38.000Z","msg":"一早已經係 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/232519_b83422bd76522e79deabea977c00e37a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F232519_b83422bd76522e79deabea977c00e37a.gif&h=68d8587b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/232520_b98aa7052580a8d6d54719e7c852e8c1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F232520_b98aa7052580a8d6d54719e7c852e8c1.gif&h=b4145605&s={SIZE}\" /